      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">Get in <span class="gradient-text">Touch</span></h1>
        <p class="text-stone-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">Whether you're a first-time landlord or managing a portfolio, we're happy to chat - no obligation.</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="card"><h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-stone-900">ğŸ  Landlords</h3><p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mt-1">Need management support? We'll assess your needs and provide a tailored proposal.</p></div>
